Ketsu-Go - The battle for Tokyo 1.2

The high command of the American forces in the Pacific has finally decided to accomplish the Operation Downfall, the invasion of the main Japanese islands, to end with the Second World War. While the Americans are going to launch their operations, the Japanese High command has his own plans; the Ketsu-Go, which is a special plan to protect the sacred Japanese islands...

As Japanese commander, inflict as much casualities as possible to the Americans... as American commander, drive your soldiers to the Imperial Palace in Tokyo!.

Autor: Santiogo Fuertes

Konversion in OG: M. Kessler

